      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface reflects a standard of excellence rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. For the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection, this acquisition represents a definitive benchmark in both aesthetic quality and mechanical integrity.",
